  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the addition of cisplatin to first-line chemotherapy
      with gemcitabine in elderly patients with non small cell lung cancer in terms of overall
      survival.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
